## Import

OIDC dynamic clients can be imported using their client ID:

```shell
terraform import ory_oidc_dynamic_client.example <client-id>
```

**Note:** When importing, `client_secret`, `registration_access_token`, and `registration_client_uri` will not be available since these are only returned at creation time.

